3. IMPLEMENTATION SUMMARY
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  MigrationFeatureExtractor:  @Component; injects @Qualifier("codeEmbeddingModel") EmbeddingModel. extractFeatures(ParsedClass) → 1088-dim: 1024 embedding + 64 handcrafted (reactive ops, framework annotations, injected fields, method count, reactive return flag, HTTP endpoints, Kafka flag, interfaces, LOC, max reactive complexity).
  MigrationClassifier:        @Service @ConditionalOnBean(codeEmbeddingModel). Loads ONNX from props.gnn().classifierModelPath() when set; else classifierModel=null, fallback only. classifyReactiveComplexity(ParsedClass) — timer flowforge.classifier.reactive.latency; ONNX inference argmax → ReactiveComplexityClass; on exception or null model uses fallbackClassification. Fallback: max method ReactiveComplexity → NONE→TRIVIAL, LINEAR→LOW, BRANCHING→MEDIUM, COMPLEX→HIGH; confidence 0.5. Implements AutoCloseable.
  MigrationClassificationService: @Service @ConditionalOnBean(MigrationClassifier). classifySnapshot(UUID, List<ParsedClass>) — classify each, group by difficulty, minio.putJson evidence/classification/{snapshotId}.json; counters flowforge.classification.total, flowforge.classification.difficulty (tag level).
  TrainingDataGenerator:       @Component @ConditionalOnBean(JavaParser). generate(Path labelledDataPath, Path outputPath) — read JSONL (source_path, difficulty, source), parse with JavaParser + MicronautCodeVisitorBridge, extract features, write JSON with "features" (float[][]) and "labels" (int[]).

